This follows a bilateral meeting that was held between South African President, Cyril Ramaphosa, and the Prime Minister of Japan, Shinzo Abe, on June 29, prior to the G20 Osaka Summit. 

The leakage of plastic waste into the environment, including the marine environment, is an issue of global concern. 

